# Styling Conventions & Design System

## Tailwind CSS v4 Configuration
- Custom CSS variables defined in [globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css)
- **Use semantic color classes**: `bg-accent`, `text-brand`, `bg-soft`, `text-charcoal`
- **Avoid arbitrary values**: Prefer `bg-accent` over `bg-[var(--accent)]`
- Container max-width: `1200px` (defined as `--container`)

## Color System
```css
:root {
  --bg: #ffffff;        /* bg-bg */
  --charcoal: #333333;  /* text-charcoal */
  --soft: #f9f9f9;      /* bg-soft */
  --footer: #111111;    /* bg-footer */
  --accent: #2ae394;    /* bg-accent, text-accent */
  --brand: #00A86B;     /* bg-brand, text-brand */
}
```

## Typography
- Font: DM Sans (weights: 300, 400, 500, 600, 700)
- Headings: `font-weight: 600`, `letter-spacing: -0.02em`, `line-height: 1.2`
- Body text: `line-height: 1.6`
- Use semantic heading tags (`h1`, `h2`, etc.)

## Button System
- **Base class**: `.btn` (44px height, 10px border-radius, flexbox centered)
- **Primary**: `.btn-primary` (brand green with shadow and hover effects)
- **Ghost**: `.btn-ghost` (transparent with white text, for dark backgrounds)
- **Hover effects**: Transform and shadow changes for premium feel

## Glass Morphism Effects
- **Transparent**: `.glass-transparent` (for hero navbar)
- **Solid**: `.glass-solid` (backdrop-blur with white background)
- Used primarily for navigation states

## Layout & Spacing
- **Container**: `container mx-auto px-4` for consistent max-width
- **Sections**: Use `py-16` for vertical spacing
- **Scroll margin**: `scroll-mt-24` for anchor navigation offset

## Animations & Transitions
- **Motion library**: Framer Motion for complex animations
- **CSS transitions**: `transition-all duration-300` for hover effects
- **Hover transforms**: `hover:-translate-y-1`, `hover:scale-105`
- **View transitions**: CSS-based with optimized timing functions

## Responsive Design
- **Mobile-first**: Use `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:` breakpoints
- **Viewport units**: `h-[100svh]` for full-height sections
- **Flexible layouts**: Combine flexbox and grid as needed

## Accessibility
- Include `aria-label` for icon buttons
- Use `aria-hidden` for decorative elements
- Ensure focus states with `focus-visible:ring-2`
- Alt text for all images

## Performance Optimizations
- **Hardware acceleration**: `transform: translateZ(0)` for animated elements
- **Will-change**: Applied to view transition elements
- **Passive event listeners**: For scroll handlers
- **Image optimization**: WebP format preferred, include `priority` for above-fold